Package AssociationRules.mappers

AssociationRules.mappers contains all mapper classes of the application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssociationMapper
    AssociationMapper is the mapper used for extraction of the association rules.
    CandidateMapper
    CandidateMapper is the mapper used for the frequent itemset extraction.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AssociationMapper.Counters
    Enumerator keeping count of the total key, value pairs that have been written to the context
    CandidateMapper.Counters
    Enumerator keeping count of the following: Inputlines: count of processed baskets Items: number of distinct items found. Writtensets: all sets that have been written to the context Rejected_wl: all sets that have been rejected due to the whitelist Rejected_size: all sets that have been rejected, because their size was smaller than the current TUPEL_SIZE
